---
import { MaskedHeading } from "@/components/typography/masked-heading";
import website from "@/assets/images/services/website.png";
import mobile from "@/assets/images/services/mobile.png";
import branding from "@/assets/images/services/branding.png";
---

<section id="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
      <MaskedHeading className="animate-slide-in opacity-0 max-w-4xl">Our Services and Products</MaskedHeading>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-12 grid-rows-12 h-[50rem] w-full max-w-[72rem] gap-6 mt-16">
        <article class="animate-slide-in opacity-0 [--slide-in-delay:150ms] col-span-3 row-span-8 bg-card rounded-xl text-center px-6 py-8 flex flex-col gap-1.5 border relative overflow-hidden">
          <img src={branding.src} alt="branding" class="absolute -top-20 left-0" />
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mt-auto text-foreground z-10">Branding</h3>
          <p class="z-10 text-sm text-foreground/75">Branding involves defining and communicating your company's values, mission, and visual identity through logos, colors, and design elements.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="animate-slide-in opacity-0 [--slide-in-delay:200ms] col-span-6 row-span-4 row-star-1 col-start-4 bg-card rounded-xl text-left py-6 px-8 flex flex-col justify-center gap-1.5 border relative overflow-hidden">
          <img src={website.src} alt="branding" class="absolute top-0 right-0 h-full w-auto" />
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-foreground z-10">Web Applications</h3>
          <p class="z-10 text-sm text-foreground/75 max-w-64">Web applications include portfolio websites, e-commerce platforms, CRM systems, ticketing websites, and restaurant ordering applications.</p>
        </article>
        <article
          class="animate-slide-in opacity-0 [--slide-in-delay:250ms] col-span-6 row-span-4 row-star-5 col-start-4 bg-card rounded-xl text-right py-6 px-8 flex flex-col justify-center items-end gap-1.5 border relative overflow-hidden"
        >
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-foreground z-10">Graphic Design</h3>
          <p class="z-10 text-sm text-foreground/75 max-w-64">Graphic design team creates logos, marketing materials, website graphics, and social media content for a consistent visual identity.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="animate-slide-in opacity-0 [--slide-in-delay:300ms] col-span-3 row-span-8 row-start-1 col-start-10 bg-card rounded-xl text-center px-6 py-8 flex flex-col gap-1.5 border relative overflow-hidden">
          <img src={mobile.src} alt="branding" class="absolute top-4 right-0 w-11/12 h-auto" />
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mt-auto text-foreground z-10">Mobile Applications</h3>
          <p class="z-10 text-sm text-foreground/75">High-quality iOS and Android apps with platform-specific languages, rigorous testing, and ongoing maintenance ensure seamless functionality.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="animate-slide-in opacity-0 [--slide-in-delay:350ms] col-span-4 row-span-4 bg-card rounded-xl text-center px-6 py-6 flex flex-col gap-1.5 border relative overflow-hidden">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mt-auto text-foreground z-10">Enterprise Applications</h3>
          <p class="z-10 text-sm text-foreground/75">Expert in full-stack development for custom software solutions, responsive design, comprehensive upgrades, and code audits.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="animate-slide-in opacity-0 [--slide-in-delay:400ms] col-span-4 row-span-4 bg-card rounded-xl text-center px-6 py-6 flex flex-col gap-1.5 border relative overflow-hidden">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mt-auto text-foreground z-10">Social Media Managers</h3>
          <p class="z-10 text-sm text-foreground/75">Results-driven social media strategy elevates your brand narrative and fosters audience engagement from awareness to conversion.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="animate-slide-in opacity-0 [--slide-in-delay:350ms] col-span-4 row-span-4 bg-card rounded-xl text-center px-6 py-6 flex flex-col gap-1.5 border relative overflow-hidden">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium mt-auto text-foreground z-10">Automation</h3>
          <p class="z-10 text-sm text-foreground/75">Automating Excel spreadsheets with VBA macros, formulas, and pivot tables streamlines data processing and visualization tasks.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
